listitem.para:
Physical Moment is a measure of the character's movement rate. Is
                            derived from PST and PEN and racial modifiers. 
                                (PST+PAG)/5 x {Racial Modifier}

A measure of the characters rate of movement in the purely mental
                            realms of psionics, magery, and computer interfaces. 
                                 ((MST+MAG)/5) x {Racial Modifier}
